    An appender that writes log messages to files.
    FileAppender$
    Companion object for FileAppender class.

    Responsible for writing log messages to a file param: path path where the log file will be created param: category category of the log messages
    FilesAppender
    Responsible for creating an FileAppenderHelper which manages the file resource param: path log file path param: category log category

    StdOutAppender$
    Companion object for the StdOutAppender class.
